game.name: Two Wheeler Trauma
game.description:
Being stuck in a traffic jam can make you feel low. However, if you are riding your own two-wheeler, chances are that you can easily squeeze through it by navigating your bike in between cars and people that are available around the heavy traffic. In this free online racing game ? Two Wheeler Game ? you also have to avoid potholes to make an easy win.   

Everyone wants to reach his/her home timely after having a long busy schedule at work. This has created a heavy traffic on the road and you are stuck in this traffic. Opt for the vehicle, which is flexible to use. You can operate your vehicle with the help of left and right, up and down keys in this cool flash game. Also, try to open your mind while avoiding the potholes and bystanders on the road. Apart from this, many other vehicles are also out there to give the traffic threat. Don?t hit them. 

You will get a chance to attain different score at each level. In Two Wheeler Trauma game, faster you will complete the level, the higher bonus you will be rewarded at the end of this cool racing game for kids. This will also result in helping you to get the highest score finally. Your aim is to navigate your bike properly through the traffic while taking care of the obstacles like pedestrians and potholes along the way. Good luck to ride safely and earn the maximum possible points. Use the space to move on and ride your motorcycle like you have not ever run.
